<plot>Top Slopes goes inside the world famous ski resorts around the country and looks at what makes these scenic wonders so famous. From the great skiing, to the fine dining, Top Slopes will highlight the best winter resorts has to offer. The show also looks at what little things make these places so special; for example, a restaurant two gondolas away that sits at 13,000 feet at Keystone.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?613025</url></doc>
